other_tests.findings: Bibasilar dependent atelectasis; Multiple hepatic lesions including a 1.6 cm simple cyst; Fluid-filled and abnormally dilated appendix measuring up to 1.1 cm with mucosal hyperenhancement, periappendiceal fat stranding, and adjacent free fluid; 4 mm hypodensity in the upper pole of the left kidney; 1.9 cm cyst in the left ovary.
